RuneWarz is a Runescape Private Server aimed at entertainment. Made by our Development Team for players, RuneWarz aims to capture a flawless gameplay experience for it's players with features that the community wants, rather than the development team. RuneWarz has alot of features, Incluiding Minigames, Quests, Skilling, Pking, PvMing and alot more! Please stay up with our community forums to keep up with the latest news about the server! RuneWarz focuses on player satisfaction, with daily updates and a large amount of content already available! Some of the features of RuneWarz are: All skills are available for you to train! Lots of monsters to kill for loot! Custom content like minigames! Looting other players in PvP!
